{
  "stem": "39.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were in the last group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After that, there was no more ghetto in my hometown Satu Mare, Szatmarnemeti, as they called it at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, let's go there when they took us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was May 31st.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were together in the ghetto all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "May 31st, going to the railroad station, it was a beautiful day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's a four-season area.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was beginning of the summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And like in most European cities, the railroad station was at the end of the town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in order to go there, we had to walk through the whole town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All around us, like all the time, always, the heavily armed soldiers and police.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So as we walked through the city, we were allowed to take a little small luggage with us, one change of clothes and one little food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to walk through the whole city, the population just looking at us like, again, we would have come from another planet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had the yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to walk through the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We arrived to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The cattle cars are already there, these open doors waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In no time, we were pushed inside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The doors closed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were so many people in one cattle car, really crowded, squeezed together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were sitting on the floor, what else, in a cattle car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And some people were not even able to sit down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were just standing, squeezed together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Of course, there was not a real window, because cattle cars wouldn't have window.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was some little like a window, small little opening, so little light came in, but not too much.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the train started, destination unknown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, there was -- we had no toilet facilities in a cattle car.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
